title: *** Nice 2 bdrm apt with free parking big yard***
posting_body: ['Beautiful hardwood floor in this unit.', 'Bedrooms do not share a wall.', ' The location of this unit allows quick and easy access to the lakes, freeway and downtown!', 'Main floor apt is located in a duplex and is 2 bedroom one bath apt.', 'It is available from Sept 1st.', 'Ideal for family with up to 3-4 members or for roommates to share the apt.', 'Laundry inside the building and off street parking spot is available at no cost.', 'There is no garage at this location.', 'Plenty of yard at the location, fenced yard in the back of building.', 'Tenant pays for', '- Electricity', '- Heat', 'Landlord pays for', '- Water', '- Sewer', '- Trash', 'Security Deposit is one months rent due at move in along with first months rent.', 'If you meet the following conditions, feel free to apply', '-No Felonies within the past 10 years', '-No Evictions or Unlawful Detainers within the past 5 years', '-Credit Score of at least 600', '-Monthly income of at least 2.5 times the requested rent', '-At least 2 years of good rental references\ufeff\ufeff']
